name: Lioness
description:
“Today in the face of homelessness we launched a call from the LGBTTTI + populations and the general population for resistance and unity for equality.

"During the Covid-19 pandemic, violence against lesbian, gay, bisexual, trans and intersex people has not decreased, on the contrary, in some cases they have increased in the absence of conclusive results to prevent, combat and eradicate them", the organizers highlighted during the broadcast.
